[COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][B][U][SIZE="4"]About Toxic OS:[/SIZE][/U][/B][/COLOR]
Toxic OS is a custom Android ROM based on the latest Android Marshmallow (6.0.1_r46). We Keep Sources Up-to date With Cyanogenmod and AOSP This Rom is still in Beta Stage, This rom is specially Made For performance and battery life. But We are Still adding lots of New Stuffs And We Are OpenSource If
You Want You Can join Toxic OS Team For Development Contact Me on Hangouts or Pm me.

