[COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][B][U][SIZE="4"]Features:[/SIZE][/U][/B][/COLOR]
 - Expanded desktop
-  Toxic OTA
-  The Drill Logcat or gtfo in settings
-  Toxic Settings 
-  Toxic Logo in about device
-  Toxic OS boot animation
-  About Toxic OS in settings About device wit Extra Options
-  Removed Lots Of cm Stuffs
-  Toxic OS ASCII Art in Flashing
-  Toxic Version in About device
-  Cyanogenmod Theme Engine
 - Lock screen weather
 - Lock screen wallpaper changer
 - Lock screen torch toggle
 - Enable lock screen media art toggle
 - Google search bar toggle
 - Status bar brightness control
 - Full volume rocker customization
 - Increasing ring in phone and alarm
 - Status bar header QS edit button
 - OmniSwitch [COLOR="red"]Removed For Now[/COLOR]
 - Quick unlock
 - Settings dashboard organization
 - Settings dashboard switches toggle
 - Settings dashboard column configuration
 - More rotation settings
 - Wake on plug configuration
 - Ambient display notification inversion toggle
 - Heads up notifications toggle
 - Force expanded notifications toggle
 - Disable immersive messages toggle
 - Phone number lookup
 - Quick reply messaging
 - Swipe to delete in messaging
 - Even more!

[COLOR="DeepSkyBlue"][B][U][SIZE="4"]Install Instructions:[/SIZE][/U][/B][/COLOR]
*Download the ROM and GApps
*Boot into Recovery
*Wipe System, Data, Cache and Dalvik Cache
*Flash the ROM and Flash Gapps 
*Reboot 

